Odaily Planet Daily News According to the US government efficiency department DOGE, which posted on the X platform: "95 contracts were canceled, saving about $115 million (upper limit value of about $235 million), including two contracts from the US Department of Agriculture: 
- $265,000 for the "Food and Nutrition Service 3-Day Leadership Workshop" held in Atlanta; 
- $30,000 for the "Malaysia Study Tour Service".
